{"tid":898693,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Houdini 入門教學 (廣東話) on Youtube","createTime":"2018-11-12T00:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T11:13:00.000Z","uid":131100,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"797c516205365026dfc10c4515e29845ccfba836","tid":898693,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T00:22:54.000Z","msg":"今次唔講 C++,<br />\n開始左一個新系列, 由淺入深講解 Houdini 入門, 玩下 3D Animation Effects<br />\n歡迎新手, 高手一齊研究分享<br />\n<br />\n之後會陸續更新, 暫時會預大概 10 條片左右, 應該夠入門去跟其他外國 Tutorial<br />\n<br />\nHoudini Basic #001 - Basic UI, View, Select, Move Tool (廣東話, Cantonese) [簡單黎講 C++]<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/17Cv8zYKOpE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F17Cv8zYKOpE&d=7oUeHtA8e%2FA4v5G%2FuKLHJWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=32a812d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/17Cv8zYKOpE</a><br />\n<br />\nHoudini Basic #002 - Poly Model (廣東話, Cantonese) [簡單黎講 C++]<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/P7-DOsZFwFs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FP7-DOsZFwFs&d=7oUeHtA8e%2FA4v5G%2FuKLHJWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=57a5a98c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/P7-DOsZFwFs</a>"},{"pid":"8687bb9e9dfd6eb0afd6d38c98cb4420d7bf64d7","tid":898693,"uid":23225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T20:39:19.000Z","msg":"估唔到有人開post講<br />\n自學緊fx 無program底有啲難入手"},{"pid":"499c2bda62c026eccb3cdb9a10f942503ea1f1c9","tid":898693,"uid":51762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T07:11:01.000Z","msg":"可唔可以教下networking 同埋點整multiplayer game"},{"pid":"d40121232e8cc90974a8a1dae87347ad8043b40c","tid":898693,"uid":207005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T07:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77ce151f448d12e463135b6eb89fc465ada4852","tid":898693,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8687bb9e9dfd6eb0afd6d38c98cb4420d7bf64d7","tid":898693,"uid":23225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T20:39:19.000Z","msg":"估唔到有人開post講<br />\n自學緊fx 無program底有啲難入手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T13:23:43.000Z","msg":"的確入門比較難, 而且講入門 Resource 唔多<br />\n無 program 底係會難少少, 不過都唔係下下要用到<br />\n我之後會慢慢講點用 script, 會當睇既完全無 program 底<br />\n不過就算會講解都好, script or math 都要自己另外去加強, <br />\n我一個人好難講得晒"},{"pid":"31d208af63c3a1ce189e29195ed6626272a21adb","tid":898693,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"499c2bda62c026eccb3cdb9a10f942503ea1f1c9","tid":898693,"uid":51762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T07:11:01.000Z","msg":"可唔可以教下networking 同埋點整multiplayer game"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T13:28:53.000Z","msg":"之前有個系列講過 Network <br />\nSocket 講起, 直到識自己整 Simple Http Web Server<br />\n又講點用 binary packet 同 protobuf<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WD-REpG29KQ&amp;list=PLeGk08zVu455jjJgP2iyaML4pP3nNGlNy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWD-REpG29KQ%26list%3DPLeGk08zVu455jjJgP2iyaML4pP3nNGlNy&d=7oUeHtA8e%2FA4v5G%2FuKLHJWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6b4064ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WD-REpG29KQ&amp;list=PLeGk08zVu455jjJgP2iyaML4pP3nNGlNy</a><br />\n<br />\nMulti-player game 其實比較難講, 因為個個 Game 既要求唔同<br />\n所以點解多數既 Game Engine 都係 Rendering 多, <br />\nNetwork Game 好難整一個 Framework fit 唔同 Game<br />\n<br />\n不過只要有一定 Network 底, 要寫簡單既唔難<br />\nAdvance 既 topic 可以 facebook inbox 問我,<br />\n可以俾到相關既 Book / Paper 你"},{"pid":"b863f3bc1d635321cea3fce660b6a10c540ee710","tid":898693,"uid":28307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T13:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c137aae149a162d0020c6ce3de39bf7ec69cc899","tid":898693,"uid":136952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T1