a900822647aed09bfd76345","tid":898693,"uid":23225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6374fa47b38f8716790652a6e0cd908e0e858742","tid":898693,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8735ca1bfb52e2f831395107597fa16865079530","tid":898693,"uid":23225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T16:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用unity呢啲engine寫定點 負責coding果啲？ 對呢方面都幾有興趣知多啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T16:53:05.000Z","msg":"主要係 coding, 有時用 Game Engine 上面砌 game logic<br />\n又時就改 engine source code 加功能<br />\n<br />\nGame Engine 就好幾隻都用過 Unity, Unreal 又或者公司自家既都有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T21:56:56.000Z","msg":"巴打都幾勁 點跳到出外國做？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T02:09:26.000Z","msg":"咁就說來話長, 做左十年, 有 D 經驗,<br />\n就試下外國咁囉<br />\n<br />\n不過依十年, 都花幾多時間自己學唔同既野 (你睇我個 Youtube Channel 都會見到學過下 D 咩)<br />\n之後做下 D Hobby Project 練習下,<br />\n當然仲有工作上有唔同既實戰經驗, 打人工又有, Free Lance 又有"},{"pid":"fea647d1f9f22561501ec4f084807aebaca058c7","tid":898693,"uid":213196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T02:35:13.000Z","msg":"外國寫game好唔好pay?<br />\n香港好多師兄都好似做狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f55e6af85a7fbe1354a6a719575c1bf9e6bccc","tid":898693,"uid":131100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fea647d1f9f22561501ec4f084807aebaca058c7","tid":898693,"uid":213196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T02:35:13.000Z","msg":"外國寫game好唔好pay?<br />\n香港好多師兄都好似做狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T03:06:02.000Z","msg":"好唔好 pay 就個個唔同<br />\nTax 高, 減返唔一定搵得多過香港<br />\n不過會有多 D 福利, 例如退休保障<br />\n少好多 OT, 多返 D 尊重似返個人唔係做狗<br />\n另外就係公司選擇同 scale 都由好細到好大都有<br />\n亦可以專心做好一個 Area"},{"pid":"81de6b2f96532ab993e0e891fa0bd9e6285fd95c","tid":898693,"uid":23225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2508ebcab87e8f7697d77e7aaa1d61e652b6